# Sectoral overlay fallbacks live under ./overlays/. The directory is kept
# in tree so the OverlayProvider can still serve aquaculture/MPA/seagrass
# polygons when the public WFS endpoints are unreachable. There is no SST
# fixture here — the SST cube is read from the on-disk Zarr cache populated
# by the startup prefetch and lazy-fill from Copernicus Marine.
